# Content plugin runtime data
content-plugin/data/draft-queue/
content-plugin/data/autopilot-state.yaml
content-plugin/data/instagram-watchlist.yaml
content-plugin/content/

# Marketing plugin runtime data
marketing-plugin/data/campaigns/
